The '''Greenhand family''' was a minor family originated by [[Holman the greenhanded]], a [[Hobbiton]] gardener. The last known of the Greenhands was apparently Holman's grandson and namesake, [[Holman Greenhand]], but the family's gardening tradition was carried on by his apprentice, [[Gaffer Gamgee|Hamfast Gamgee]]. No other descendants of the family are documented.<ref name="long">{{App|Gamgee}}</ref>

